# go.sum is present even though this module has zero external dependencies.
# This satisfies static analysis rules (e.g. SonarQube text:S8566)
# that expect a dependency lock file to be committed for reproducibility
# and supply-chain protection.
#
# No actual checksums are needed here because there are no 'require' entries
# in go.mod. See: https://go.dev/ref/mod#go-sum-files
